# XelloxShop Environment Variables
# Copy to .env và chỉnh sửa trước khi deploy

# Flask Security
SECRET_KEY=sk-your-super-secret-key-here-32+characters-long

# SMTP Email (Railway compatible)
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587          # Fallback: 465 (SSL)
SMTP_USER=your@gmail.com
SMTP_PASS=ktxq zybj aigw msfo  # ✅ GMAIL APP PASSWORD (16 ký tự)
SMTP_SENDER=\"Xellox Shop\" <your@gmail.com>

# Shop Settings
SHOP_NAME=\"Xellox Shop\"
SUPPORT_EMAIL=cskt1009@gmail.com
SUPPORT_PHONE=0967427517
SUPPORT_FB=https://fb.com/yourshop

# File Storage
UPLOAD_DIR=./uploads
DATA_DIR=./data
CLOUDINARY_URL=cloudinary://api_key:api_secret@cloud_name  # Optional - Cloudinary cho Railway

# MBBank (Optional)
MB_USERNAME=your_mb_username
MB_PASSWORD=your_mb_app_password
MB_ACCOUNT_NUMBER=your_account_number

# Railway Volume mount (if used)
# DATA_DIR=/data
# UPLOAD_DIR=/data/uploads

## 🚀 Railway SMTP Setup:
1. Vào https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
2. App: \"Mail\" | Device: \"XelloxShop\"
3. Copy 16 ký tự App Password → paste vào SMTP_PASS
4. Test: POST /api/test-smtp {\"to_email\":\"test@gmail.com\"}

## ⚠️ Railway Port Issues:
- Nếu 587 fail → thử SMTP_PORT=465
- Logs Railway: Check [SMTP AUTH ERROR] hoặc connection timeout

